{"about_the_game":"<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1492300/extras/inv_gif_menu.gif?t=1724734829\" /><br>Invirium is an action shooter game with randomly generated levels and elements from the roguelike genre. You are the cell that needs to eliminate dangerous pathogens in the human body. During the gameplay, you'll find interesting items that will help you upgrade/add new abilities to fight against tons of microorganisms.<br><br><strong>MICROORGANISM</strong><br>You will find a lot of inner body enemies like bacterias, viruses, or fungus. Be patient and vigilant against them - each has unique qualities which might annihilate you.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1492300/extras/inv_gif_boss.gif?t=1724734829\" /><br><br><strong>ORGANS</strong><br>You will lurk many organs like the intestines, kidneys, or liver to eliminate pathogens. Explore and find life references to the human body.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1492300/extras/inv_gif_kidney.gif?t=1724734829\" /><br><br><strong>MEDICAL NEWS</strong><br>Apart from cool gameplay, you can find useful information about medical news in this game world &quot;Virofarium&quot; and more!<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1492300/extras/inv_gif_virof.gif?t=1724734829\" />","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/1492300?t=1724734829","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1492300/page_bg_raw.jpg?t=1724734829","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1492300/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1724734829","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1492300/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1724734829","categories":[{"desc